# 📋 GIGASHIELD — Master Task File

> `[ ]` Not started | `[/]` In progress | `[x]` Completed
> **P0** Critical | **P1** Important | **P2** Nice-to-have
> Each task has: Priority, ID, Description, Owner, Dependencies, Acceptance Criteria, Est. Hours

