## PHASE 3 — MVP BUILD (Days 8–20)

### Sprint 3A: Core Infrastructure (Days 8–13)

- [ ] **P0** `3A.1` — **Set up PostgreSQL with schema + seed data**
  - Owner: Backend Eng | Depends: `2B.1` | Est: 3h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] All tables created via migration files (not raw SQL)
    - [ ] Seed script: 500 workers, 25 zones, 100 historical triggers, 50 past policies
    - [ ] Database runs in Docker container
    - [ ] Connection pooling configured (pg-pool)

- [ ] **P0** `3A.2` — **Implement worker registration API**
  - Owner: Backend Eng | Depends: `3A.1`, `2B.2` | Est: 4h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] POST /workers/register creates worker + auto-assigns zone (nearest by lat/lng)
    - [ ] Phone uniqueness enforced
    - [ ] OTP simulation (always accepts 123456 for demo)
    - [ ] Response includes recommended plan from Shield-SAC
    - [ ] Input validation (Joi/Zod schema)
    - [ ] Unit tests: valid registration, duplicate phone, invalid input

- [ ] **P0** `3A.3` — **Implement policy subscription API**
  - Owner: Backend Lead | Depends: `3A.2` | Est: 4h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] POST /policies/subscribe creates 7-day policy
    - [ ] Calls Shield-SAC for dynamic premium (or uses cached price)
    - [ ] Policy status lifecycle: PENDING → ACTIVE (on payment) → EXPIRED (after 7 days)
    - [ ] Pool discount applied if worker is in Shield Pool
    - [ ] Cannot subscribe if active policy exists
    - [ ] SHAP explanation stored in policy record

- [ ] **P0** `3A.4` — **Implement Shield-SAC pricing microservice**
  - Owner: ML Eng | Depends: `1B.1`, `2B.2` | Est: 10h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] FastAPI service with POST /calculate endpoint
    - [ ] Trained on synthetic data (50,000 worker-weeks) — training completes < 4h
    - [ ] OR fallback: XGBoost model trained (< 10 min) with fairness post-processing
    - [ ] Shield mechanism: premium hard-capped at 5% of weekly earnings
    - [ ] SHAP values returned with every premium
    - [ ] Inference latency < 200ms (measured via /health endpoint)
    - [ ] Unit tests: fairness constraint never violated across 1000 random inputs

- [ ] **P0** `3A.5` — **Implement DSI calculation service**
  - Owner: ML Eng | Depends: `1C.2` | Est: 4h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] FastAPI service with GET /dsi/:zone_id endpoint
    - [ ] Computes DSI from weather (OWM), traffic (mock), orders (mock)
    - [ ] Returns score 0-100 + breakdown of 3 sub-scores
    - [ ] Caches result in Redis (TTL 5 min)
    - [ ] GET /dsi/heatmap returns all zones with current DSI

- [ ] **P0** `3A.6` — **Implement parametric trigger engine**
  - Owner: Backend Eng | Depends: `1C.1`, `3A.1` | Est: 6h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Polls weather API every 5 minutes per zone
    - [ ] Evaluates 5 individual trigger thresholds + DSI composite
    - [ ] On trigger: creates record in `triggers` table + emits event to message queue
    - [ ] Deduplication: same trigger type for same zone within 6 hours = 1 trigger
    - [ ] POST /triggers/inject for demo (creates trigger immediately)
    - [ ] Logging: every poll logged with raw data

- [ ] **P0** `3A.7` — **Build React PWA shell and design system**
  - Owner: Frontend Lead | Depends: `2C.1`, `2D.1` | Est: 6h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] React 18 + Tailwind CSS 3 project initialized
    - [ ] Router: React Router v6 with 6 routes (onboarding, home, storm, payout, history, pool)
    - [ ] Design system: color palette (shield blue/green/orange/red), typography, spacing
    - [ ] Component library: Button, Card, Badge, Modal, ProgressBar, StatusIndicator
    - [ ] Mobile-responsive layout (PWA manifest configured)
    - [ ] Service worker for offline capability

- [ ] **P0** `3A.8` — **Integrate weather API pipeline**
  - Owner: Backend Eng | Depends: `3A.6` | Est: 3h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] OpenWeatherMap current weather + forecast for 25 zones
    - [ ] Rate limiting: ≤ 60 calls/min (batch zones with nearby coords)
    - [ ] Response normalized to internal format (mm, °C, AQI)
    - [ ] Mock mode: returns simulated data for demo (controllable via env var)

### Sprint 3B: Intelligence & Automation (Days 14–20)

- [ ] **P0** `3B.1` — **Implement zero-touch claim automation**
  - Owner: Backend Lead | Depends: `3A.6`, `2A.3` | Est: 6h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Trigger event → find all active policies in affected zone
    - [ ] For each policy: create claim record (status: INITIATED)
    - [ ] Call PADS fraud validation (parallel)
    - [ ] If fraud_score < 0.3: AUTO_APPROVE → initiate payout
    - [ ] If fraud_score ≥ 0.7: AUTO_REJECT → log reason
    - [ ] If between: FLAG → log for manual review
    - [ ] Duplicate prevention: UNIQUE (policy_id, trigger_id) constraint
    - [ ] End-to-end target: trigger → payout initiation < 60 sec

- [ ] **P0** `3B.2` — **Implement PADS fraud detection service**
  - Owner: ML Eng | Depends: `2B.2` | Est: 8h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] FastAPI service with POST /validate endpoint
    - [ ] 5-layer pipeline implemented:
      - [ ] Layer 1: Device check (emulator/root detection) — binary
      - [ ] Layer 2: GPS-IP consistency (Haversine + IP geolocation) — distance-decayed
      - [ ] Layer 3: IMU kinematic validation (accelerometer + gyroscope) — ensemble
      - [ ] Layer 4: Duplicate claim check (DB query) — deterministic
      - [ ] Layer 5: Behavioral anomaly (Isolation Forest) — trained on seed data
    - [ ] Weighted aggregation: final fraud_score 0.0-1.0
    - [ ] All 5 check results logged to fraud_logs table
    - [ ] Unit tests: clean claim passes, GPS spoof fails, emulator fails

- [ ] **P0** `3B.3` — **Implement Razorpay instant payout**
  - Owner: Backend Eng | Depends: `3B.1` | Est: 4h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Razorpay Payout sandbox integration (not production)
    - [ ] Payout to UPI ID (vpa)
    - [ ] Webhook handler: payout.processed → update payouts table → update claim status to PAID
    - [ ] Error handling: payout.failed → retry once → flag for manual
    - [ ] Razorpay ref stored in payouts table
    - [ ] End-to-end: claim approved → UPI credit < 3 min

- [ ] **P0** `3B.4` — **Implement XAI dashboard component**
  - Owner: ML Eng + Frontend Eng | Depends: `3A.4`, `3A.7` | Est: 5h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] SHAP waterfall chart component (Recharts or custom SVG)
    - [ ] Shows top 5 factors for selected worker's premium
    - [ ] Positive factors (increase premium) in red/orange
    - [ ] Negative factors (decrease premium) in green
    - [ ] Fairness constraint visualization (max allowed vs actual)

- [ ] **P1** `3B.5` — **Implement WhatsApp onboarding bot**
  - Owner: Frontend Lead | Depends: `1B.3`, `3A.2` | Est: 6h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Webhook receives WhatsApp messages
    - [ ] Conversation state machine: language → name → platform → earnings → subscribe
    - [ ] Hindi and English conversation flows working
    - [ ] Calls /workers/register API on completion
    - [ ] Sends premium recommendation back via WhatsApp
    - [ ] Error handling: invalid inputs prompt retry

- [ ] **P0** `3B.6` — **Implement worker home screen**
  - Owner: Frontend Eng | Depends: `3A.7`, `3A.4`, `3A.5` | Est: 5h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Shield status badge (ACTIVE / EXPIRED / NONE)
    - [ ] Current premium and coverage amounts
    - [ ] 7-day risk forecast (DSI scores, color-coded)
    - [ ] Zone name and risk level
    - [ ] Shield Pool info (if joined)
    - [ ] Quick actions: view claims, view payouts, view ROI
    - [ ] Data refreshes on screen focus

- [ ] **P0** `3B.7` — **Implement Storm Mode screen**
  - Owner: Frontend Eng | Depends: `3B.1`, `3A.7` | Est: 4h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Auto-activates via WebSocket/polling when trigger fires for worker's zone
    - [ ] Shows: trigger type, DSI score, progress bar (4 steps)
    - [ ] Steps: Trigger detected ✓ → Claim created ✓ → Fraud check ✓ → Payout processing...
    - [ ] Expected payout amount and ETA
    - [ ] Hindi motivational message at bottom
    - [ ] Transitions to payout confirmation screen on completion

- [ ] **P0** `3B.8` — **Implement payout confirmation screen**
  - Owner: Frontend Eng | Depends: `3B.3`, `3A.7` | Est: 2h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Amount credited in large font
    - [ ] Razorpay reference number
    - [ ] Trigger reason (e.g., "Heavy Rain — Andheri West")
    - [ ] Time elapsed (trigger → payout)
    - [ ] Share button (WhatsApp share)

- [ ] **P1** `3B.9` — **Implement Shield Pool feature**
  - Owner: Backend Eng + ML Eng | Depends: `2C.1`, `3A.3` | Est: 5h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] POST /pools/join — create pool in zone or join existing
    - [ ] Premium recalculated with pool discount (15-20%)
    - [ ] Pool page shows: members, total fund, discount %
    - [ ] When trigger fires: all pool members get claims created
    - [ ] Minimum 3 members to form pool

- [ ] **P0** `3B.10` — **Implement demo control panel**
  - Owner: Frontend Lead | Depends: `3A.6` | Est: 3h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Admin-only page (no auth, just hidden URL for demo)
    - [ ] Button per trigger type: Rain, Flood, Heat, Pollution, Curfew
