## PHASE 4 — POLISH, TESTING & DOCUMENTATION (Days 21–28)

### 4A. Testing

- [ ] **P0** `4A.1` — **End-to-end integration test: happy path**
  - Owner: All Team | Depends: Phase 3 | Est: 3h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Onboard worker → subscribe → inject trigger → claim auto-created → fraud passes → payout sent
    - [ ] Each step verified: correct data in DB, correct API responses, correct UI state
    - [ ] Total time measured (target < 3 min)

- [ ] **P0** `4A.2` — **Edge case testing**
  - Owner: QA / All | Depends: `4A.1` | Est: 4h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] Duplicate trigger: worker gets only 1 claim per trigger
    - [ ] Expired policy: no claim created
    - [ ] Spoofed GPS: PADS rejects claim
    - [ ] Emulator detection: PADS rejects claim
    - [ ] Multiple triggers same zone: worker gets highest payout only
    - [ ] Pool payout: all members receive claims correctly
    - [ ] Premium > 5% earnings: shield caps correctly

- [ ] **P1** `4A.3` — **Load test: 100 concurrent workers**
  - Owner: DevOps + Backend | Depends: `4A.1` | Est: 3h
  - Acceptance:
    - [ ] k6 or Artillery script simulating 100 workers
    - [ ] 50 simultaneous triggers fire
    - [ ] All claims processed within 5 min
    - [ ] No 5xx errors
    - [ ] Response times documented

